OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FA mostly cloudy day with a few
OL,6,Fbright spells and showers, mainly over
OL,7,FArgyll. Showers for all parts in the
OL,8,Fevening, turning heavy with some
OL,9,Flonger spells of rain. Windy.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FCloudy
OL,12,Fand breezy on Saturday with heavy
OL,13,Fshowers clearing later in the day. Dry
OL,14,Fon Sunday and Monday with some long
OL,15,Fspells of sunshine. Becoming warmer.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
